==Bio==
David Graeber was an Anthropologist and Activist. He authored [[First Five Thousand Years of Debt|'Debt: The First 5000 Years']]. He was active in the Occupy Movement.

He died aged 59 on September 2nd, 2020. ([https://www.opendemocracy.net/en/opendemocracyuk/remembering-david-graeber-rest-power-peace-and-possibility/ Obituary from Open Democracy])

